---
title: Portuguese-Style Chicken with Potato Wedges and Pickled Red Onion Kale Salad
description: Smoked paprika and chili-garlic sauce are used as a marinade for chicken thighs, to create a smoky and spicy flavour! This pickled red onion kale salad is sweet and tangy and pairs very well with oven-baked potato wedges! Enjoy!
